{"id": 3012, "genre": 1000, "title": "当你怀念「童年」的时候，你怀念的其实是什么？", "description": "童年被人们习惯性地与“快乐”画上等号。但说到底，我们到底为什么对它念念不忘？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 18963, "comment_count": 53, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201910032245240LXTNHpQaqeYbwGn.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-04T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5945, "title": "当你怀念「童年」的时候，你怀念的其实是什么？", "content": "当你怀念「童年」的时候，你怀念的其实是什么？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 347667, "content": "没有太大压力的氛围，一种“不焦虑”的理想状态", "image": "img/option/option/20191003224604Gbjtn518NsoMERg2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347669, "content": "熟悉的生活环境（房子/食物/人）带来的亲切感", "image": "img/option/option/20191003225007bXy705AgkeIudtca.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347670, "content": "没太多复杂的需求，吃根冰棍都能开心一整天", "image": "img/option/option/20191003225028rna9FH2Z0lCEMtIo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347671, "content": "天大的事爸妈/老师都会挡着，有任性的资格", "image": "img/option/option/201910032251141hANFVX6oaHvBuqW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347672, "content": "一切都还没有定型、“什么都有可能”的希望感", "image": "img/option/option/20191003225437Y51tTZbUrBfcaQFv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347673, "content": "孩子的眼中世界比较简单，凡事不用考虑那么多", "image": "img/option/option/201910032253504OuIMrJnLN9dFRse.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347674, "content": "相对不太功利的人际关系，“朋友”真的就是朋友", "image": "img/option/option/20191003225317yvIMPxXathWzlDJE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347675, "content": "对世界有好奇心和探索欲，不像长大后那么容易丧", "image": "img/option/option/20191003225152O4qTk1mZAviDtd8P.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347683, "content": "那时候更元气，玩啥都有精神头儿（发际线也还在", "image": "img/option/option/20191003225954k3J40f5UM7Gp1EPd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347682, "content": "因为回不去才值得追忆（即使它本身并没有多美好", "image": "img/option/option/20191003224940eTREZnuqSd7zo9GO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347676, "content": "都不是，我有别的理由/不，我其实并没有很怀念", "image": "img/option/option/20191003225230iLsGZCryJYDKXjUA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}